{"tid":1162071,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"傳銷公司地址","createTime":"2019-05-19T15:19:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T11:47:34.000Z","uid":91835,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"28b07bcb00ad0893e11dbc1ca29f6e1f6f6862f7","tid":1162071,"uid":91835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T15:19:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">資料由the world巴打（#235224）提供<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n【傳銷公司資料】<br />\n地址：中匯商業大廈20樓<br />\n<br />\n公司分咗以下幾條Team<br />\nInfinite Team<br />\nMarvel Team<br />\nKJ Team<br />\nChampion Team<br />\nAC Team<br />\n<br />\nAC team地址：旺角恒利中心三樓一出lift門對住個間<br />\n<br />\n公司有一個文化 叫「大家好文化」 當有人要做sharing嘅時候，就會講聲大家好 其他人跟住就要回應好！！！！！ 「大家好！」 「好！！！！！」<br />\n<br />\n佢地有個勁「正面」嘅concept，叫做「加減乘除人」<br />\n<br />\n加人：正面、積極<br />\n乘人：有成就嘅人<br />\n減人：負面、唔主動<br />\n除人：最worst、無貢獻嘅人<br />\n<br />\n另外會講乜嘢八二定律，八成人幫緊兩成人做野，點樣好好利用人地既時間幫自己搵錢，點樣唔好再成為八成人<br />\n<br />\n【仲有講每個職級都有相對既百分比分成】<br />\n1.Advisor <br />\n2.Supervisor <br />\n3.Consultant <br />\n4.TeamLeader <br />\n5.Director<br />\n<br />\n【以下係相關產品資料】<br />\n<br />\n美容：<br />\n雅蘭15樓<br />\n佐敦新貿中心14樓<br />\n銅鑼灣世貿22樓<br />\n<br />\n教育：<br />\n英文：信和9樓<br />\nPlaygroup: 太子柏宜7-9樓<br />\n投資：潮特4-5樓<br />\n<br />\n【Marketing】<br />\n公司主力Sell既兩樣野 - 教育同美容<br />\n<br />\n例給教育係Sell：Finance, 英文課程, PlayGroup導師班etc.<br />\n<br />\n美容就係：喺兩間美容院有好多好正既療程<br />\n<br />\n總之你搵到人簽單你就有佣分，冇記錯佢仲有Sell中醫調理<br />\n<br />\n升學嘅話就係幫一間叫hkue(新名：uche)嘅垃圾私校做，得hotel management 同marketing 揀，但以我所知大部分人讀完出黎同冇讀過冇分別 <br />\n<br />\n佢地仲有開啲類似enrichment course 咁嘅夜校課程(校名分別係AMEC，動向教肓中心-ACEC，亞洲管理教育中心)，分別有英文（Cosmo英文進修），投資，同埋幼教。除左投資有少少用之外其他都冇乜用。<br />\n<br />\n教育既Center<br />\n佢地有3個Center，一個喺太子，<br />\n另外兩個分別喺潮流特區同信和搭𨋢上去<br />\n<br />\n佢地旺角有兩間分店美容院<br />\n一間係會Sell到你仆街同個Friend比人Sell上去做到爛面爛足半年<br />\n既 垃圾Nuskin(旺角同銅鑼灣)<br />\n一間係喺雅蘭中心，叫new skin lab<br />\n另一間叫pretty renew。<br />\n好似仲有一間中醫美容院<br />\n<br />\n【美容雞查詢系統】<br />\n<a href=\"http://beautychicken.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbeautychicken.com&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ1%2BoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=a1edb6e3\" target=\"_blank\">http://beautychicken.com</a><br />\n<br />\n有新資料可以SEND去 beautychicken420@gmail.com 或者 Add New"},{"pid":"06e3d45cfe040c719c186c7822d73dd373e8d857","tid":1162071,"uid":91835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T04:22:54.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"f39380c54d441884d0281e10856c9a181d248bef","tid":1162071,"uid":121247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T04:27:26.000Z","msg":"杜sir幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b8a168cebf11f8dfa1f044fa262f1e22f3d570b","tid":1162071,"uid":91835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f39380c54d441884d0281e10856c9a181d248bef","tid":1162071,"uid":121247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T04:27:26.000Z","msg":"杜sir幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T06:48:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a91190c150d8842c2473b16e61d90d52a618df75","tid":1162071,"uid":91835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T07:47:48.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"50bb8ed3fd57bfa6ca4b1620b7e9ab74be023213","tid":1162071,"uid":91835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T08:31:47.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"ce2cd7aaa8d4979ef6f652d72f4630a6b3a285e6","tid":1162071,"uid":91835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T19:39:40.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"227321c2e20704e08b16852f6ce84eaaaa82ebfb","tid":1162071,"uid":235224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:47:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}